<item>
            <title>[LU-1936] filter_obd::fo_read_cache:1... should be marked as unsigned</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1936</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;filter_obd::fo_read_cache:1... should be marked as unsigned, being signed causes confusion for users/admins when they get output like:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;$ lctl get_param obdfilter.*.read_cache_enable&lt;br/&gt;
obdfilter.testfs-OST0000.read_cache_enable=4294967295&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;instead of the expected 0 or 1.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
